Comfortable 1-bedroom apartment with a panoramic view of Warsaw, Mokotów- Wilanowska subway station
Advantages:
• Wilanowska subway station (750 m), Służew subway station (750 m), 15 minutes to the city center;
• bus stop (170 m), bus line: 108, 139, 200, 217, 251, 339;
• access to commercial infrastructure: Żabka (170 m), Biedronka (400 m), Mokotów Shopping Mall (1900 m);
• recreation areas: Królikarnia park (1350 m) and Dolinka Służewska park (1100 m).
Layout:
• spacious living room with a sofa bed and fully equipped kitchenette;
• bedroom with a double bed, built-in wardrobe and separate working space;
• bathroom with a shower cubicle, built in furniture and washer-dryer;
• hallway with a built-in wardrobe;
• balcony with rattan furniture and an unique view.
Facilities:
• air-condition;
• monitoring and security 24/7;
• reception, gym, sauna and viewing terrace on top of the building;
• green patio with a playground and stone grill;
• underground parking and a bike room.
Rent conditions:
Rental cost – PLN 4400;
Administrative rent – PLN 1200;
Media advances per 1 person – PLN 200;
Internet and TV on one’s own;
Security deposit – PLN 5600;
Institutional lease agreement for a time period of 12 or more months.
Parking place included in the rental cost.
It is possible to rent a second parking place for PLN 400 per month.
For a single or a couple, non-smoking and without pets.
Available for rent from 14.02.2025.
